Name: ezstr
Version: 0.2
Summary: No more tostring boilerplate
Home-page: https://github.com/MichaelVerdegaal/ezstr/archive/0.2.tar.gz
Author: Michael Verdegaal
Author-email: michaelverdegaal@hotmail.nl
License: MIT
Description: # ezstr
        
        Ezstr gives you a quick way to create a str representation method for your python class, as this can quickly become a hassle with a lot of attributes.
        
        # Usage
        
            from ezstr import tostr
            
            @tostr
            class MyClass:
        	    ...
        
